{"name":"Athletics","type":"skill","img":"icons/skills/movement/feet-winged-boots-brown.webp","data":{"difficulty":"basic","type":"move","cost":{"trained":"200","plus10":"400","plus20":"600"},"stat":{"str":true,"tou":false,"agi":true,"wfr":false,"wfm":false,"int":false,"per":false,"cr":false,"ch":false,"ld":false},"description":"<p>Athletics is the acrobatic and tactical movement skill that allows characters to make balanced and poised movement. Athletics have two sections: Agility- and Strength-based movement.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>STRENGTH:</strong> Athletics Strength is a character's ability to climb, swim, and other strength-based physical activities.</li>\n<li><strong>AGILITY:</strong> Athletics Agility is a character's ability to balance, jump, catch landings, and move about a battlefield or training course.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<h3>Athletics Concealment</h3>\n<p>Another use for Athletics Agility is to move silently amongst the battlefield. If a character is attempting to move silently, they roll Athletics. For every degree of success, the opponents gain a -5 on their hearing check.</p>","characteristic":{},"data":{"description":"<p>This is the description.</p>"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"an9AAnyv69VtBEmg":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.k913vheZuFYJxB2g"}},"_id":"uehjQcoyKy0qZN61"}
{"name":"Camouflage","type":"skill","img":"icons/magic/perception/silhouette-stealth-shadow.webp","data":{"difficulty":"basic","type":"field","cost":{"trained":"200","plus10":"400","plus20":"600"},"stat":{"str":false,"tou":false,"agi":false,"wfr":false,"wfm":false,"int":true,"per":true,"cr":false,"ch":false,"ld":false},"description":"<p>The Camouflage Skill is used to hide items and equipment or to conceal the character's person. Using Skill requires an appropriate environment to mask whatever is in question. Camouflage is opposed to any opponent's Investigation Skill, and if the character does not have Investigation, use the Perception Characteristic.</p>\n<p>Camouflage represents an active effort to foil an opponent's investigation attempt.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"an9AAnyv69VtBEmg":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ji38mzo4wKX1CEXK"}},"_id":"wSUAN3SKI9Pv49Yc"}
{"name":"Cryptography","type":"skill","img":"icons/commodities/tech/console-steel.webp","data":{"difficulty":"adv","type":"field","cost":{"trained":"0","plus10":"0","plus20":"0"},"stat":{"str":false,"tou":false,"agi":false,"wfr":false,"wfm":false,"int":true,"per":false,"cr":false,"ch":false,"ld":false},"description":"<p>The use of the Cryptography Skill allows characters to encrypt and decrypt codes and frequencies, as well as hack and bypass systems. Skill Tests are not required to either leave or read basic messages and codes, but are necessary to communicate or decipher complicated messages. Use this Skill alongside the Cyber Warfare section of the Handbook.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"an9AAnyv69VtBEmg":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.scxL4ZfJc4c4BLjK"}},"_id":"NW4wp0F9Wxt2qKdo"}
{"name":"Command","type":"skill","img":"icons/environment/people/charge.webp","data":{"difficulty":"basic","type":"social","cost":{"trained":"0","plus10":"0","plus20":"0"},"stat":{"str":false,"tou":false,"agi":false,"wfr":false,"wfm":false,"int":false,"per":false,"cr":false,"ch":false,"ld":true},"description":"<p>Command is the ability to effectively lead others. Command deals with any character giving orders to another.</p>\n<p>If two opposing commands are being made to counteract each other, the GM may allow the characters to choose whom to follow, or have the two commands roll as an opposing test.</p>\n<p>The Command Skill Test also uses the same type of example modifiers shown in the **Appeal** Skill Description. If a command is suicidal or not in the best interests of the overall picture, the test automatically gains a -60 penalty.</p>"},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"an9AAnyv69VtBEmg":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.hpkGnNgbNjIFnneV"}},"_id":"WJYvJJS6ZtTtdVyj"}
